                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-326632720" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-326632720" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="326632720">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/suimolim/">Frank Zephyr</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2011-04-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读之前期望有点高。这本书既不像文物资料，也不算风物考据。东拼西凑的，有点文抄的味道。当然，我这么说未免太刻薄了些，里面可取的东西还是有的，只是我个人不大喜欢这种风格而已。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
